# Phase 2 — GitHub Actions

Planned workflows:
- `ci.yml` — on PR/push: lint (ruff + npm lint), build matrix (api + frontend), trivy scan, push to ECR with OIDC
- `deploy.yml` — on push to main: update image tag in `k8s/`, trigger ArgoCD sync
- `terraform-apply.yml` — on tag push: plan + apply (bonus, proper GitOps for infra)

Auth: OIDC role, no static AWS keys.
